    <adgm-expansion-panel   deeplink="guidance-for-applicants" 
        type='plus' variant='primary'>                    <adgm-text slot="title" variant="textL" weight="400">
                        <h3>Guidance for applicants</h3>
                    </adgm-text>
        
<div>        <adgm-body  variant="textS"><p><span>The guidance for applicants provides information on completing the application to register an entity in ADGM and should be read in conjunction with the relevant legislation. The Guidance Notes do not cover other requirements as set out in the relevant legislation such as contact with the court and other internal obligations that a company will need to consider and carry out.</span></p></adgm-body>
