                            <h3>Code of Market Conduct (&quot;CMC&quot;)</h3>
                        </adgm-text>

                            <adgm-text variant="textXS" italic="">

                                        Published 26 Sep 2022
                                    
, 
                                        Updated 26 Sep 2022
                                                                </adgm-text>
                    </adgm-flex>

                    <adgm-flex gap="rBodyXS">
                            <adgm-text variant="textS">
                                <p><p><span>The purpose of the Code of Market Conduct ("CMC") is to supplement the Market Abuse provisions in Parts 8 and 9 of the Financial Services and Markets Regulations 2015 ("FSMR").</span></p></p>
