                    <adgm-flex gap="rBodyXS">
                            <adgm-text variant="textS">
                                <p><p><span>This Joint Guidance proposes practical solutions to manage the impact of economic uncertainty on Expected Credit Loss, while remaining compliant with globally accepted financial reporting standards, IFRS. It is suggested to employ the flexibility embedded in the IFRS 9 framework to cope with the COVID-19 crisis.</span></p></p>
