                    <adgm-flex gap="rBodyXS">
                            <adgm-text variant="textS">
                                <p><p><span>This Confidentiality Policy provides guidance concerning the obligations and requirements on the Financial Services Regulatory Authority (the &ldquo;Regulator&rdquo;) when using and disclosing non-public information provided by third parties in the course of regulating financial services in the Abu Dhabi Global Market (&ldquo;ADGM&rdquo;).</span></p></p>
